      "span_text": "Suppose K is shifted but I(K) is not shifted. Then there exists x, y, f 1 , f 2 ∈ I(K) such that xf 1 , yf 2 ∈ I(K) and yf 1 , xf 2 / ∈ I(K), where x and y are vertices and f 1 and f 2 are faces, see [CITATION_1] ."
